<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Villes — Vigie BC</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,500;9..144,600;9..144,700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="/css/Style_woah.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
<div class="onboarding" data-onboarding-step>

  <div class="onboarding__top">
    <a href="/" class="brand"><span class="brand__mark"></span> Vigie BC</a>
    <a href="{{ path('dashboard') }}" class="onboarding__skip-all">Passer la configuration →</a>
  </div>

  {% include 'onboarding/_steps.html.twig' with {'active': 4} %}

  <div class="onboarding__body">
    <div class="wizard-card">
      <div class="eyebrow">Étape 4 sur 5</div>
      <h2>Dans quelles villes cherchez-vous des opportunités ?</h2>
      <p>Nous ne vous alerterons que pour les BC publiés dans ces villes.</p>

      <div class="search-box" style="max-width:none;margin-bottom:14px;">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7"/><path d="M21 21l-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Rechercher une ville…" data-option-search="[data-city-list]">
      </div>

      <form method="post" action="{{ path('app_choose_cities') }}">
        <div class="option-list" data-selectable data-city-list>
          {% for city in cities %}
            <label class="option-row" data-option-name="{{ city.name }}">
              <input type="checkbox" name="cities[]" value="{{ city.name }}">
              <span class="check"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></span>
              <span>{{ city.name }}</span>
            </label>
          {% else %}
            <p style="font-size:13.5px;color:var(--ink-400);">Aucune ville disponible pour le moment.</p>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <span class="wizard-selected-count" data-selected-count>{{ selectedCities|length }} sélections</span>

        <div class="wizard-footer">
          <a href="{{ path('app_choose_nature') }}" class="btn btn-outline">Retour</a>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;">
            <button type="submit" name="skip" value="1" class="btn btn-ghost">Passer cette étape</button>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Continuer</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
 <script src="/js/app_woah.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
